Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藤田  藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天助我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早出现在山麓驻扎处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.62,0:02:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正飞车赶来我们这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.73,0:02:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已不是以前的绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么短的时间\N他究竟做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.12,0:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是传说中的绯村剑心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.73,0:02:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐马车来访\N好像大官驾到的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已决定重回江湖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十五话 炼狱战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.69,0:03:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你抓来的张十刀透露的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.52,0:03:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早我们抓到\N另一个志志雄的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还让我们看了他们准备\N火烧京都的计划信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.73,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们决定今晚\N十一时五十九分开始行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.71,0:03:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论志志雄有多厉害\N但一定寡不敌众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.75,0:03:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此他们必需采取\N突击和暗杀的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.85,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照理说像张十刀\N口风这么紧的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会  这么轻易就此招供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他会那么快\N就将计划告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么高见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们将火烧京都的秘密\N泄露给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是别有居心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  行动就要开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有必要再继续躲藏此处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要藉着我们的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒沉睡已久的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.63,0:04:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓别有居心是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.66,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄的目的\N不外是复仇和窃国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他还有其他\N我们不知道的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.85,0:04:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德川庆喜将军\N由大阪坐船逃回江户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,官军才得以大获全胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许志志雄这次\N也想利用这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来个措手不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都大火只是\N他们作战的第一阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.47,0:05:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘船由海上炮击东京\N才是他们真正的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.77,0:05:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火烧京都只是\N分散我们的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪那么简单\N就泄露情报给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.32,0:05:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他们的目标\N是在首善之都东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就被他们骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在一定已经出发了\N我们要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又想放我鸽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一次不会让你如愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助  你怎么在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么在这里问你绯村剑心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓越帮越忙真是一点也没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.85,0:05:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间紧迫了  还不快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到大阪用走的吗  笨蛋坐马车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙真是噜嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.26,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马车快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直奔大阪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别嗦  安静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都现有五千警力\N人数是志志雄的数十倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是为防止京都起火\N而部署的人力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早的密报信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那封计划信是不是有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.57,0:06:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们派了几乎\N全部的警力在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只为了阻止京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是从以前到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都一直是志志雄的反攻重镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人力本来就都聚集在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对  是帮主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.21,0:07:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机关枪一把要多少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.25,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说机关枪是火力强大的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.39,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打败志志雄\N就得添购这种装备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许机关枪是\N攻击力强大的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们真正的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.97,0:07:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许并非是这些武器\N所能替代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你千万别不看自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真正的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.55,0:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N我相信我们会成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剑心写来的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.47,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天路上那么多警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火烧京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一团乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.61,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是今天才开始一团乱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以帮主命令你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要阻止火烧京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快以飞鸽传书联络京都那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近江女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家换好衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要采取行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦  我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.85,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们在东京和苍紫决斗时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.22,0:09:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾立誓与御庭帮  誓不两立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  大家动作快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在人手几乎全分配在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大阪方面不可能再增加人手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.87,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且无论马车多快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到大阪一定已超过\N十二点以后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要再找志志雄的下落\N一定会来不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.78,0:09:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这嗦  就会有办法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使东京被志志雄炮击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.39,0:09:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会那么简单就给打烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们既然来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和他们直接上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢再打一次试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋\N你不讲话没人把你当哑巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.81,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助\N你不要小看志志雄的破坏力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.85,0:10:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉永六年浦贺冲就是藉着舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能成为开国天皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从幕府末年到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.86,0:10:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东京人民一直\N活在不安恐惧之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.86,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使到今天\N仍禁不起一点的伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.50,0:10:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,些许的炮击\N就会造成东京的大混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以现在政府的力量\N根本毫无招架的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东京马上会成为无法地带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.62,0:10:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  只要能拦截志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能阻止这一切发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再迟就来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的经验\N志志雄行动的条件有二个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个是利用夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个就是利用混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前志志雄就是利用\N这两个方法来达成他的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这家伙一定\N也是想利用这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.27,0:11:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混水摸鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.54,0:11:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这家伙的船一定是\N混在靠岸的民家渔船内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.96,0:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄先生\N我们这次的计划很周详
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心到现在\N都没发现我们的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使他们现在发现也来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许现在他们已经知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这次的计划很秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.58,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是究竟这艘船\N是什么样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.22,0:12:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是想看看这艘船的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心里在想什么  我全知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然早晚都要看到\N我现在就带你去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们最后的王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它叫做炼狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎样  由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治  几点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十一点二十二分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离火烧京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有三十七分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.48,0:13:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了  火怎么还没起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.42,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.66,0:13:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市内大批警力部署\N我们人手遭遇阻拦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么遇到这种情况  真伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  必需变更作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去放火  我去解决他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务\N只是暗杀高官要员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.05,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不需要杀死警官和人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.82,0:14:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大火一烧\N所有的人都是死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别想阻拦我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.86,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来我也不必顾虑太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.43,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我啊我我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋别跟来  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这些家伙看看\N我们警察的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀队  前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  他们人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你们这些胆小鬼往哪里逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.78,0:15:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我大镰刀的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我蝙也在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮你们掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还不快进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕  坚守到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.93,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N我们趁现在全面进攻警备队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.61,0:16:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  找到放火的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.78,0:16:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.22,0:16:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁  究竟想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操  不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是御庭帮的新帮主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人都被我们解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.14,0:16:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家还要保持高度警戒才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我们就照原定计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好防火和防卫准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.05,0:16:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮主你也小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到御庭帮这么受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.27,0:17:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是出人意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.14,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是老翁十年来努力的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮的实力  还是很坚强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他们勇敢的样子就可以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.35,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭帮将来一定会有所作为的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.57,0:17:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是你这个小鬼在搞乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.39,0:18:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么慢\N京都方面究竟在搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.83,0:18:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到现在火还没放起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方有五千警力\N多少都得花点功夫收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过也太慢了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.37,0:18:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必太着急  所谓欲速则不达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.35,0:18:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是志志雄\N能说出这么有哲理的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.92,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是作战\N但想到故居被火烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心中仍有些许不舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心还是太软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必再为莫须有的理由感伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.66,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快搭我们的战舰出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们胜利的焰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他的决斗还未一决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不禁令人感到遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火点起来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.16,0:19:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没  有一辆超快速的马车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄的船在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  那艘木船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.84,0:19:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个烟就是准备出航的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.85,0:19:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是什么大军舰\N没想到是艘破船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.92,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,载我都载不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙  在这干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄先生  我们被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧曾是最亲近的战友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.11,0:20:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么了解我的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.58,0:20:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道现在就要提前决斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.55,0:20:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在时间紧迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.22,0:20:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间和这些人搅和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治  全体进入舰内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.36,0:20:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们阻挡不了我的\N你们等着看我胜利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须潜水靠近船身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后从船底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.58,0:20:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要挖洞不能用刀剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来东京时 身上带了炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.42,0:20:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不用点火的最新型炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.89,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个嗦的男人\N到底对我哪里不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.77,0:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不用点火\N在海里炸弹也无法引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.87,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹在海里 是起不了作用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.71,0:21:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就在这乖乖的\N等大阪警备队来就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.28,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别轻举妄动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会饶你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄的船爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是船出问题了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.14,0:22:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搭乘恐怖的炼狱之船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到东京来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.81,0:22:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家等着看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.61,0:22:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼狱的真面目吧
